{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"19547-bbalgan-yeon","title":"빨간 연","description":"책을 열어 연을 찾아 보아요. 빨간 연에 대해 읽어보고, 왈리 그림체도 즐겨 보아요.","language":"Korean","langCode":"ko","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sunny Hsiao"],"illustrators":["Jeyanthi Manokaran"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/19547-bbalgan-yeon"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117638/size3/ac6a77ff9d0dd2a0a61098ad0557ff0c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117638/size6/ac6a77ff9d0dd2a0a61098ad0557ff0c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33712/size6/44f1bbc4c8f7c4bdc3497f956efb8f25.jpg","text":"얘들아 저것봐! 연 싸움이야!\n아이쿠! 보라색 연은 찢어졌네.\n어이쿠! 노란색 연은 멀리 날아갔고.\n오호라! 빨간색 연은 무사히 내려오고 있어!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33713/size6/743edc4a30edf345d970adee29e85839.jpg","text":"서둘러! 빨리 뛰어봐!\n이번엔 안에 들어가 숨어봐.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33714/size6/9df3bb3bffafe0b12f9f10d521f791f5.jpg","text":"멈추지 않고 달리고,\n미끄러지듯 요리조리 피해봐!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33715/size6/73ddad45c74d370e3fedf4d9f8ee569d.jpg","text":"건초를 얹을 새도 없게\n수레를 몰고,\n단숨에 뛰어 내려서 \n장터 사이로 \n쏜살같이 달려봐!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33716/size6/effedb7cc52780fc8da91de7e2a91c59.jpg","text":"부딪히지 않게 조심하고,\n계속해서 달리는 거야!\n더욱 더 빠르게, \n쏜살같이 나아가!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33717/size6/5aefa5f8c26904fac0601451261c0198.jpg","text":"우와! 야호! 내 것이다!\n빨간 연은 이제 나의 것이야!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33718/size6/75cc01b368448df630e9146bf5805f41.jpg","text":"아니?!\n또 달려야 하나?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":69}}